## Direction Status Tracker

| Direction | Status | Evidence | Exploration |
|---|---|---|---|
| Phase 0 definition gate for a tiny delayed trigger | CLOSED | Exploration 001 showed the only canonical exact trigger object is the prior five-role helical singleton object with `a3` highlighted by extra observables; it is not a genuinely narrower trigger-only object. | Exploration 001 |
